  вҡ  oxc(no-this-in-exported-function): `this` should not be used in exported functions
   в•ӯв”Җ[no_this_in_exported_function.tsx:1:37]
 1 в”Ӯ export function foo() { console.log(this); }
   В·                                     в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
   в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
  help: Remove `this` or convert to a non-exported function. In bundlers, `this` becomes `undefined` in exported functions.

